HEADWORD: Zama
<hw>Za"ma</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>prop. n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>the
battle in 202 BC in which Scipio decisively defeated Hannibal at the end
of the second Punic War.</def>⟦br⟧
